<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَبِثَ سَنْبَتاً من الدَّهْرِ و <span class="c2">(٧)</span> سَنْبَتَةً: أي حِقْبَةً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وناقَةٌ سَبَنْتَاةٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span>: أي جَرِيْئةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والسَّبَنْتى:</span> اسْمٌ للنَّمِرِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">البُسْتَانُ:</span> كَلِمَةٌ مُعَرَّبَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(٧) سقط حرف العطف من م.<br>(٨) في ك: سبنتاء.</p> </div>